.IX Xref "CPPLAST"
.IX Item "CPPLAST"
This symbol is intended to be used along with \f(CW\*(C`CPPRUN\*(C'\fR in the same manner
symbol \f(CW\*(C`CPPMINUS\*(C'\fR is used with \f(CW\*(C`CPPSTDIN\*(C'\fR. It contains either "\-" or "".
.ie n .IP """CPPMINUS""" 4
