.IX Item "HAS_MODFL"
This symbol, if defined, indicates that the \f(CW\*(C`modfl\*(C'\fR routine is
available to split a long double x into a fractional part f and
an integer part i such that |f| < 1.0 and (f + i) = x.
.ie n .IP """HAS_NAN""" 4
