\&\f(CW\*(C`CALL_CHECKER_REQUIRE_GV\*(C'\fR flag for backward-compatibility.  The effect
of that flag setting is that the check function is guaranteed to get a
genuine GV as its \f(CW\*(C`namegv\*(C'\fR argument.
