can set or clear the \f(CW\*(C`SV_GMAGIC\*(C'\fR and/or SV_SMAGIC flags, to specify which
magic to handle or not handle; whereas plain \f(CW\*(C`sv_vcatpvfn\*(C'\fR always specifies
both 'get' and 'set' magic.
