deprecated \f(CW\*(C`PERL_VERSION\*(C'\fR to using this macro:
.Sp
.Vb 1
\& #if PERL_VERSION <= 9
.Ve
.Sp
becomes
.Sp
.Vb 1
\& #if PERL_VERSION_LE(5,9,\*(Aq*\*(Aq)
.Ve
